NORTH CAROLINA DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
v.
Kenneth SHIELDS. No. 60P16. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 13, 2016. Tamika L. Henderson, Assistant Attorney General, for NC Department of Public Safety. Michael C. Byrne, for Shields, Kenneth.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 23rd of February 2016 by Petitioner in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 13th of April 2016."
